        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellTop\">Duarte Barbosa</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellTop\">captain of the “Trinidad”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Juan Serrano</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">captain of the “Concepcion”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Luis Alfonso de Gois</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">captain of the “Victoria”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Andres de S. Martin</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">pilot of his Majesty</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Sancho de Heredia</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">notary</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Leon de Ezpeleta</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">notary</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Pedro de Valderrama</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">priest</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Francisco Martin</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">cooper</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Simon de la Rochela</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">calker</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Cristóbal Rodriguez</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">steward</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Francisco de Madrid</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sobresaliente and soldier</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Hernando de Aguilar</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">servant of Luis de Mendoza</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Guillermo Fenesi or Tanaguì</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">gunner of the “Trinidad”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Anton Rodriguez</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sailor</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Juan Sigura</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sailor</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Francisco Picora</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sailor</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Francisco Martin</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sailor</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Anton de Goa</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">common seaman</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Rodrigo de Hurrira</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">common seaman</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Pedro Herrero</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sobresaliente</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Hartiga</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sobresaliente</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Juan de Silva, Portuguese</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">sobresaliente</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Nuño</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">servant of Magallanes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Henrique, from Málaca</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">servant of Magallanes and interpreter</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Peti Juan, French</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">servant of Magallanes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Francisco de la Mezquita</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">servant of Magallanes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellBottom\">Francisco</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellBottom\">son-in-law of Juan Serrano</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p>All of these names are to be found in Navarrete’s list. See <i>ante</i>, note 26.</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p><sup><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000000171\">362</$link></sup> <i>Chiacare</i>: the nangca; see <span class=\"sc\">Vol. XXXIV</span>, p. 107, where Pigafetta describes and names this fruit. Mosto confuses it with the <i>durio xibethenus</i>, which is abundant in the western islands of the Indian <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a>archipelagoes, Mindanao being the only one of the Philippines where it is found (Crawfurd, <i>Dictionary</i>); but it is the <i>Artocarpus integrifolia</i> (see <span class=\"sc\">Vol. XVI</span>, p. 88, note 72). MS. 5,650 makes this “capers.”</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p><sup><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000000171\">363</$link></sup> MS. 5,650 omits mention of the panicum, sorgo, garlic, and nangcas.</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
