        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p><sup><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000000178\">470</$link></sup> “Mauzor” in Eden (p. 259).</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p><sup><$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000000178\">471</$link></sup> MS. 5,650 does not mention the “quintalada.” The quintalada was a per cent of the freight or of the lading space of the ship allowed the officers and crew of sailing vessels. The amount allowed to each of the officers and crews of Magalhães’s fleet was specified in section 74 of the instructions given by Cárlos I to Magalhães and Falero at Barcelona, May 8, 1519. The amounts (see Navarrete, iv, pp. 150–152) are as follows:</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"blockquote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"blockquote\"><p class=\"first\"><i>Following are declared the quintaladas which shall be laden in the ships about to sail to the spice regions, and the amount which each one shall lade, from which he will pay the twenty-fourth part to his Highness.</i></p></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"blockquote\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellTop\"></td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellTop c2\">Quintaladas</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">First, Fernando de Magallanes and Falero, captains-general of the said fleet will be allowed sixty quintals of cabin space [cámara] apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">60</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\"><i>Item</i>: of quintalada, and twenty quintals apiece, these twenty to be stowed below decks, and the cabin space above decks</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">20</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The other three captains shall each be allowed forty quintals of cabin space, ten of them quintalada</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">40</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Treasurer, twenty quintals of cabin space, and one quintalada below decks</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">22</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Accountant, a like amount of twenty-two quintals</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">22</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Notaries of the ships, fifteen [<i>sic</i>] quintals of cabin space and one quintalada</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">22</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Alguacil of the fleet, six quintals and one quintalada</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The sailors of the ships, one and one-half quintalada</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Chaplains, four quintals apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Physician and surgeon, five quintals apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Masters and pilots, twelve quintaladas of cabin space and one quintalada apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">14</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Boatswains, eight quintals of cabin space and one quintalada apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Sailors, one quintalada apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Common seamen, one and one-half quintals apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1½</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Boys, three arrobas of quintalada apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">3 arrobas</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft c2\">Gunners</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The master gunners, three quintals of cabin space apiece and one quintalada</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The other gunners, one and one-half quintaladas apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2½</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Carpenters, one and one-half quintaladas</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2½</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Calkers, the same</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2½</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Coopers, the same</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2½ <a class=\"x-ebookmaker-pageno\"></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Crossbowmen, the same</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2½</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Servants of the captains, one quintalada apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Stewards, three quintals apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellBottom\">Stonecutters, three quintals apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellBottom\">3</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p>In case that our service is performed by building a fortress there, the persons abovementioned who shall remain in it, shall be allowed the said quintaladas in the ships that shall come [to these kingdoms], and they shall receive also a like sum annually from the quintaladas that shall remain there.</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p>If a fortress be made, our captain shall appoint such persons with the duties and functions that shall be necessary in the said fortress, and shall appoint them the competent recompense until we appoint to those duties.</p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><p><i>Chests</i></p></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\">\n</div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\"><table>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellTop\">The captains-general shall take four chests, on which they will pay only the twentieth</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellTop\">4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The other captains shall take three chests apiece on the same terms</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Accountant and treasurer two chests apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The notaries of the ships one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Masters and pilots, each one chest</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Boatswains, one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Alguacil of the fleet, one chest</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Chaplains, one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The merinos of the fleets, one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The captains’ servants, one chest for each two</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Physician and surgeon, one chest</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Sailors, one chest for each two</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Common seamen, one chest for each two</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Boys, one chest for each three</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Master gunners of the ships, each one chest</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">The other gunners, one chest for each two</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Carpenters, calkers, coopers, masons, crossbowmen, and sailors, one chest for each two</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft\">Stewards, one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"cellLeft cellBottom\">Sobresalientes, one chest apiece</td>\n<td class=\"cellRight cellBottom\">1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-0d454f twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-5fae15 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-1a3ef0 twpub-c6b43ad861391ea7-6b4cd0\"><div class=\"back\"><div class=\"div1 notes\"><div class=\"divBody\"><div class=\"table\">\n</div></div></div></div></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/c6b43ad861391ea7/text/000001368": {
